---
const whatsapp = "https://wa.me/18492507070?text=Hola%2C%20quiero%20cotizar%20una%20entrega";
---

<footer class="relative py-16 lg:py-20 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-ink dark:bg-black" />
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_bottom_left,_rgba(193,18,31,0.08),transparent_60%)]" />
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-[1400px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-brand flex items-center justify-center text-white font-black">IW</div>
          <span class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Imperio W</span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-[35ch]">
          Distribución de arena azul, itabo, grava y empaque. Entregas con camiones de 17, 18 y 20 mt³ a toda la República Dominicana.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">Contacto</h4>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm text-white/70">
          <a href="tel:+18292597070" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-brand transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 6.75c0 8.284 6.716 15 15 15h2.25a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25v-1.372c0-.516-.351-.966-.852-1.091l-4.423-1.106c-.44-.11-.902.055-1.173.417l-.97 1.293c-.282.376-.769.542-1.21.38a12.035 12.035 0 0 1-7.143-7.143c-.162-.441.004-.928.38-1.21l1.293-.97c.363-.271.527-.734.417-1.173L6.963 3.102a1.125 1.125 0 0 0-1.091-.852H4.5A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 4.5v2.25Z"/></svg>
            +1 (829) 259-7070
          </a>
          <a href="https://maps.google.com/?q=San+Cristobal+Republica+Dominicana" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-3 hover:text-brand transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-brand shrink-0" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 10.5a3 3 0 1 1-6 0 3 3 0 0 1 6 0Z" /><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M19.5 10.5c0 7.142-7.5 11.25-7.5 11.25S4.5 17.642 4.5 10.5a7.5 7.5 0 1 1 15 0Z" /></svg>
            San Cristóbal, RD — Ver mapa
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-white uppercase tracking-[0.15em]">Enlaces</h4>
        <div class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <a href="#materiales" class="block text-white/70 hover:text-brand transition-colors">Materiales</a>
          <a href="#flota" class="block text-white/70 hover:text-brand transition-colors">Flota</a>
          <a href="#cobertura" class="block text-white/70 hover:text-brand transition-colors">Cobertura</a>
          <a href={whatsapp} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="block text-brand hover:text-brand-light transition-colors font-semibold">Cotizar entrega</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10 text-center text-xs text-white/50">
      &copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Imperio W. Todos los derechos reservados.
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
